<headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 08 at 2:27AM EDT  by NWS Cleveland</headline>
<description>...Areas of fog early this morning...
Areas of fog will continue to expand across Northeast Ohio and
Northwest Pennsylvania through sunrise. Visibilities are
fluctuating and will occasionally drop to a quarter mile or less,
especially in valleys and low lying areas. Motorists should use
caution and be prepared to slow down if they encounter fog.</description>
